DOC.brief_summary: This study will evaluate the effectiveness and benefit of treatment with onabotulinumtoxinA in Chronic Migraine patients who have received a minimum of 7 treatment cycles.
DOC.brief_title: A Retrospective Study to Evaluate the Effectiveness and Benefit of onabotulinumtoxinA in Patients With Chronic Migraines
DOC.criteria: 15 or more headache days over a 30 day period A minimum of 7 treatment cycles with onabotulinumtoxinA Any treatment cycle dose of onabotulinumtoxinA greater than 200 units
